Source: edge-gfx-dkms
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Intel Graphics <linux-intel-graphics@intel.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: edge-gfx-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms (>= 3.0), build-essential, curl, git, patch, xz-utils, zstd, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SR-IOV i915 DKMS source package
 DKMS source package for the Intel i915 GPU driver with SR-IOV support.
 Builds i915 and kvmgt kernel modules from a vendored kernel.org LTS
 i915 snapshot with a curated SR-IOV patch stack applied at build time.
 .
 SR-IOV patches are fetched from a configured quilt repository during
 the DKMS pre-build hook. The quilt URL and branch are set in quilt.conf.
 .
 Supported kernel series: 6.18.x
